<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Abraham's Blog</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/</link><description/><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 11 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.inshomepgup.com/tags/vue/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Vue3 特性学习</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vue3/vue3-%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</link><pubDate>Wed, 11 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vue3/vue3-%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</guid><description>&lt;p>从Vue2 过渡到Vue3，有挺多方面还是不一样的，大部分还是提升了效率，可以更专注于业务的开发。&lt;/p></description><category>Vue</category><category>Vue</category><category>Vue3</category></item><item><title>Vue3插槽的使用</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vue3/vue3%E6%8F%92%E6%A7%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</link><pubDate>Wed, 11 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vue3/vue3%E6%8F%92%E6%A7%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="插槽">插槽
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>组件的灵活性很大一部分都来源于插槽（Slot），这大大提升了组件的可复用性和扩展性。它允许父组件在子组件的预留位置中插入任意内容。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>在React里，类似的功能是通过 &lt;code>props.children&lt;/code> 实现的，可以直接将JSX片段作为属性传递。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="默认插槽">默认插槽
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>当子组件只定义一个匿名插槽时，父组件传递的所有内容都会被放置在这个插槽中。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>子组件 (&lt;code>ChildComponent.vue&lt;/code>)&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">class&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;default-slot&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">h3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>子组件标题&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">h3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">p&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>如果父组件没有提供内容，我将作为后备内容显示。&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">p&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>父组件使用&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">ChildComponent&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">p&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>这是从父组件传递过来的内容，它将替换掉子组件的后备内容。&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">p&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">ChildComponent&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="具名插槽">具名插槽
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>当我们需要在子组件的不同位置插入不同内容时，就需要使用具名插槽。通过为 &lt;code>slot&lt;/code> 元素添加 &lt;code>name&lt;/code> 属性，我们可以定义多个插槽。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>子组件 (&lt;code>LayoutComponent.vue&lt;/code>)&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">class&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;container&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">header&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;header&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">header&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">main&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c">&amp;lt;!-- 这是一个默认插槽 --&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">main&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">footer&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;footer&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">slot&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">footer&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>父组件使用&lt;/strong>
在父组件中，我们使用 &lt;code>v-slot&lt;/code> 指令并带上插槽的名字来指定内容的目标插槽。&lt;code>v-slot&lt;/code> 有一个简写形式 &lt;code>#&lt;/code>。&lt;/p></description><category>Vue</category><category>Vue</category><category>Vue3</category><category>Slot</category></item><item><title>Vue渲染机制</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/render/vue%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/render/vue%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://cn.vuejs.org/guide/extras/rendering-mechanism" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>渲染机制&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>虚拟DOM，Virtual DOM&lt;/p></description><category>Vue</category><category>Vue</category></item><item><title>Hash路由和History路由</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vuerouter/hash%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%92%8Chistory%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vuerouter/hash%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%92%8Chistory%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1/</guid><description>&lt;p>监听hash改变的函数
&lt;a class="link" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/hashchange_event" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>onHashChange&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>hash路由：
监听hash url 的变化，来渲染内容。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>history路由：
使用 History API 控制路由&lt;/p></description><category>Vue</category><category>Vue</category><category>Vue-Router</category></item><item><title>动态Router和权限控制的实现</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vuerouter/%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81router%E5%92%8C%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/vue/vuerouter/%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81router%E5%92%8C%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/</guid><description>&lt;p>在常见的管理系统中，对于页面路由的权限控制通常是在后端配置当前角色当前用户的可访问路由表。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="计划的实现效果">计划的实现效果
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>用户A - 登录 - 获取路由表 - 动态插入路由表 - 首页。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="引用资料">引用资料
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://tdesign.tencent.com/starter/docs/vue/get-started" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>TDesign-Vue&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://tdesign.tencent.com/starter/vue/dashboard/base" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>项目Preview&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>说明：启动一个空白的项目然后一步步实现。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="启动项目">启动项目
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>使用快速开始启动一个普通的模板用来实践整个过程。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/InsHomePgup/pic_go_img/main/blog/20250117164524893.png"
loading="lazy"
alt="|700x311"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h5 id="脚手架创建项目">脚手架创建项目
&lt;/h5>&lt;p>在脚手架创建项目那里，使用vue3 + vite + lite版本启动。
升级一下依赖,安装vue-router&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pnpm add vue-router
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h6 id="初始化一些基础文件">初始化一些基础文件
&lt;/h6>&lt;p>添加一些简单的用来测试路由的目录,layout部分使用基础的侧边栏，导航栏，内容区来创建。
在page下面home + about两个页面。
在layout下面添加一个default.vue
使用嵌套路由来切换页面。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="主要的api">主要的API
&lt;/h3>&lt;h5 id="动态路由">动态路由
&lt;/h5>&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://router.vuejs.org/zh/guide/advanced/dynamic-routing" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>动态路由&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">// 添加路由
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">router.addRoute({ path: &amp;#39;/about&amp;#39;, component: About })
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">// 删除路由
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">router.removeRoute(&amp;#39;about&amp;#39;)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">router.addRoute({ name: &amp;#39;admin&amp;#39;, path: &amp;#39;/admin&amp;#39;, component: Admin })
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">router.addRoute(&amp;#39;admin&amp;#39;, { path: &amp;#39;settings&amp;#39;, component: AdminSettings })
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h5 id="查看路由表">查看路由表
&lt;/h5>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">useRouter&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;vue-router&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">const&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">router&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">useRouter&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">();&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">console&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">log&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;routes&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">router&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">options&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">routes&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description><category>Vue</category><category>Vue</category><category>Vue-Router</category></item></channel></rss>